<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Verity downgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Verity downgraded.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Hambrecht &amp; Quist said it lowered its recommendation on Verity Inc to buy from strong buy.</p>
<p>-- The analyst was not immediately available to comment.</p>
<p>-- Shares were off 5/8 to 7-3/4 in early Nasdaq trade.</p>
</text>
